Method Detail

extractUpdateCode

protected String extractUpdateCode(String _origCode)
Extracts from the _origCode the update code without header. Because the configuration item update code of an page includes also the content of the page, this page content must be removed from the original configuration item code so that the update code could be extracted correct.

Overrides:
extractUpdateCode in class ExportParser
Parameters:
_origCode - original code from which the update code must be extracted
Returns:
extracted update code (without header and page content)
